# NurseAda Infrastructure Consistency

## Service Ports

| Service | Port | Env URL |
|---------|------|---------|
| Gateway | 8080 | NEXT_PUBLIC_GATEWAY_URL, EXPO_PUBLIC_GATEWAY_URL |
| CDSS | 8002 | GATEWAY_CDSS_URL |
| Knowledge | 8003 | GATEWAY_KNOWLEDGE_URL |
| XAI | 8012 | GATEWAY_XAI_URL |
| LLM | 8001 | GATEWAY_LLM_URL |
| FHIR adapter | 8011 | GATEWAY_FHIR_URL |

## Config Pattern

- Use `_url(key, default="")` for optional service URLs. Empty string = not configured.
- Add new URLs to `services/gateway/app/config.py` and `.env.example`.
- Document in `.env.example` with comment.

## Start Scripts

- Update `scripts/start-dev-all.ps1` when adding services.
- Set env vars for gateway before starting it (GATEWAY_CDSS_URL, etc.).
- Start order: CDSS → XAI → Knowledge → Gateway → Web.
